column5: Went after work to the canals and was suprised to find that the canals were frozen and the bottom of cooks bay was as well. Two boats were trying to get to the launch ramp and told me the ice was approx 1" thick. Hopefully be on the canals in a week and on the bay in 3-4 weeks. Cheers Jeff
Ohhh yeah!!  Sounds great.  Thanks for the update.
